    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Citizenships papers consisting of pre-printed documents, issued to American seamen by customs collectors from 1796 to 1940, as a result of An Act for the Relief and Protection of American Seamen of 1796.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
